## API Documetation

The api documentation can be found at `localhost:3000/api-docs`

## Prerequisites

This project requires:
* Rails 5.2
* Ruby <%= RUBY_VERSION %>, preferably managed using [rbenv][]
* PostgreSQL must be installed and accepting connections

On a Mac, you can obtain all of the above packages using [Homebrew][].

If you need help setting up a Ruby development environment, check out this [Rails OS X Setup Guide](https://mattbrictson.com/rails-osx-setup-guide).

## Getting started

Install used gems by calling:

    $ bundler install

Create database by calling:

    $ rails db:create

Migrate database by calling:

    $ rails db:migrate

Seed database by calling:

    $ rails db:seed

### Run it!

To run the application locally:

    $ rails s

